OL,3,CHospital asks visitors to wear face
OL,4,Cmasks as flu cases rise
OL,6,F"As such, we are inviting all staff,
OL,7,Fpatients and visitors to our Emergency
OL,8,FZone ` made up of the Emergency
OL,9,FDepartment, Acute Medical Unit, Acute
OL,10,FFrailty Unit, Same Day Emergency Care
OL,11,Fteam ` to wear a surgical face mask.
OL,12,FThis is to reduce the risk of
OL,13,Finfection and to enhance the safety of
OL,14,Fall concerned.
OL,16,F"We also recommend those with
OL,17,Frespiratory symptoms, such as a cough
OL,18,For a cold, to avoid visiting friends,
OL,19,Ffamily, and loved ones at our hospital.
